latestPosts.caption:
Planning my little Manyata’s birthday is always special, and this time I found the perfect place — Cake Country!
From beautifully customised cakes to a whole new range of mouth-watering pastries, this place is a dessert lover’s dream.
Tried their Red Velvet pastry and it was pure bliss!
They also have a cozy café upstairs with some really tasty fast food too.
If you’re in Jaipur, do check out Cake Country — they have branches in Murlipura and Kalwar Road.

#CakeCountry #BirthdayPlanning #CustomisedCakes #JaipurBakery #RedVelvetLove #FoodieDiaries #PastryHeaven #cafevibes
